User Registration
    ↓
Registration Form
    ↓
POST auth/register
    ↓
Validate email/password
    ↓
Hash and salt password with bcrypt
    ↓
Save user to MongoDB
    ↓
Return JWT token (for email save/remember me)
    ↓
User Login


User Login
    ↓
Post auth/login
    ↓
Compare password with bcrypt
    ↓
Return JWT token (expires in 24hrs)


User request
    ↓
Authrization Middleware
    ↓
Verify JWT
    ↓
Allow acces to route
    ↓
Controller logic
    ↓
Database
    ↓
JSON Response


Dog Adoption
    ↓
User clicks adopt
    ↓
Post /dogs/:id/adopt
    ↓
Auth Middleware
    ↓
Find Dog in database
    ↓
Update adopted status
    ↓
Save to database
    ↓
Return success response


Listing new Dogs
    ↓
User fill dog form
    ↓
Post /dogs
    ↓
Auth Middleware
    ↓
Validate Dog Data
    ↓
Save dog to database
    ↓
Return success response


View Dogs
    ↓
Get /dogs
    ↓
Auth middleware
    ↓
Fetch dogs from database
    ↓
Apply filters/pagination
    ↓
Return Dogs JSON


Removing Dogs
    ↓
User clicks Delete
    ↓
Delete /dogs/:id
    ↓
Auth Middleware
    ↓
Find dog in database
    ↓
Verify User owns dog = true
    ↓
Check if Dog is Adopted
    ↓
Delete dog
    ↓
Return success response

Pagination
    ↓
Get /dogs?page=2&limit=10
    ↓
Auth middleware
    ↓
Read query params
    ↓
Fetch limited Results
    ↓
Return paginated JSON response

Permissions/restrictions
    ↓
Verify JWT token
    ↓
Identify Current User
    ↓
Check ownership
    ↓
Allow/Deny